# CHANAKYA Radar

- AI Deal Health Board — **not** a workflow or lender-stage board.
- Dual view: **Matrix** (executive) · **Kanban** (operational) — one shared filtered dataset.
- Cards **never** draggable.
- Kanban columns fixed: On Track · Needs Attention · At Risk · Dormant · On Hold · Completed.
- Matrix cards: On Track · Needs Attention · Dormant · At Risk (View Details → Kanban focus).
- Global filters (RM · Product · Source) refresh Matrix counts, Kanban columns, and recommendations together.
- Card click opens the **Active Workspace** (Strategic Bench / Credit Bench / Loan Workspace) — CHANAKYA decides.
- Never change scoring / health classification when adding views or filters.
- Never show Rejected / Lost / Cancelled / Withdrawn / Closed lenders.
